pondus (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
        - Pondus now has an icon/logo
        - add/edit dialog: pressing 'Enter' in one of the entry fields
          has the same effect as clicking 'OK', i.e. adds/edits the
          dataset
  * debian/menu: add icon field
  * debian/rules: add dh_icons
  * Use python-support instead of python-central

 -- Eike Nicklas <eike@ephys.de>  Fri, 01 Feb 2008 20:15:52 +0100

pondus (0.0.6-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release:
        - plotting weight vs time is enabled
        - '+' and '-' can be used to increment/decrement date and weight
          in the add/edit dataset dialog
        - ',' can be used instead of '.' as the decimal separator in
          the add/edit dataset dialog
  * simplify debian/rules and debian/control
  * add debian/watch
  * do not install upstream docs and manpage as they are installed in
    upstream setup.py

 -- Eike Nicklas <eike@ephys.de>  Sun, 06 Jan 2008 23:48:11 +0100

